    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - TVS Supply Chain Solutions - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "TVS Supply Chain Solutions invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Tiruchirappalli location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout TVS Supply Chain Solutions:\nTVS Supply Chain Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with TVS Supply Chain Solutions!",
